 <name>tokenizers</name>
 <channel>pecl.php.net</channel>
 <summary>Native, byte-exact LLM tokenizer (BPE/WordPiece/Unigram) + Claude/Gemini API companion</summary>
 <description>
  A native PHP extension (C) that counts, encodes, and decodes LLM tokens,
  byte-exact with the reference tokenizers. It implements three algorithms:
  byte-level BPE (tiktoken-compatible cl100k_base and o200k_base, plus
  HuggingFace tokenizer.json BPE models), WordPiece (BERT family), and
  Unigram (T5/SentencePiece). The merge loop is O(n log n) and vocabularies
  are loaded once per worker into a process-global cache. A pure-PHP
  companion (\Tokenizers\Remote\Anthropic, \Tokenizers\Remote\Gemini,
  \Tokenizers\TokenCounter) counts Claude and Gemini tokens through the
  providers' official count_tokens APIs. Vocabulary files are downloaded and
  checksum-verified on first use; they are never redistributed with the
  package.
 </description>
