 </version>
 <stability>
  <release>alpha</release>
  <api>alpha</api>
 </stability>
 <license uri="https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0">Apache-2.0</license>
 <notes>
  Initial alpha release. Native BPE (cl100k_base, o200k_base, HuggingFace BPE),
  WordPiece (BERT) and Unigram (T5/SentencePiece) tokenizers, all byte-exact
  with their Python references. Includes \Tokenizers\Encoding (download/cache
  and tokenizer.json loader) and the standalone pure-PHP Claude/Gemini
  count_tokens companion. Requires libpcre2-8 at runtime.
 </notes>
